long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Annotating Trails is a Beta project for a Human Centered Computing course
It allows creation of a Knowledge graph like visual map of all browsed content and allows for Annotation of contenet

Created by Graduate Students at Texas A&M: Aaron Knodell, Nivedhan Manavalan, Kirthan Vasudevan and Mitchell Priour
